{"title":"SUCTF-2019-EasySQL","uid":"d3f930ca78e2fa76ff67e677ee0f9b21","slug":"SUCTF-2019-EasySQL","date":"2021-05-22T03:44:42.000Z","updated":"2021-06-15T06:13:50.128Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/SUCTF-2019-EasySQL.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqonghh3u8j30xc0hgabp.jpg","content":"<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\"/>\n\n<h2 id=\"题目页面\"><a href=\"#题目页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目页面\"></a>题目页面</h2><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr29dcadzj30qc0swq3g.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr29dcadzj30qc0swq3g\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"访问页面\"><a href=\"#访问页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问页面\"></a>访问页面</h2><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr2a5dz52j30q406ut8m.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr2a5dz52j30q406ut8m\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"分析解题\"><a href=\"#分析解题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分析解题\"></a>分析解题</h2><p>打开页面之后，没有什么思路，然后查看源代码也没有什么思路</p>\n<p>然后我就只能百度了</p>\n<p>发现了连个 payload</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>*,1</code></li>\n<li><code>1;set sql_mode=PIPES_AS_CONCAT;SELECT 1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>分别的显示结果为</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr2r0ox96j31n20ha0ta.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr2r0ox96j31n20ha0ta\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr2s1pkhgj31n60gwmxo.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr2s1pkhgj31n60gwmxo\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"题目源码\"><a href=\"#题目源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目源码\"></a>题目源码</h2><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr2tu3hssj30sz0fvac5.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr2tu3hssj30sz0fvac5\"></p>\n<p>其实主要就是 SQL 查询语句：<code>select &quot;.$post[&#39;query&#39;].&quot;||flag from Flag&quot;;</code></p>\n<p>由于题目没有过滤<code>*</code>，因此可以查询所有内容就可以拿到 Flag 了</p>\n<p>Payload:<code>*,1</code></p>\n<p>拼接后就变成了<code>SELECT * ,1 || flag FROM Flag</code></p>\n<p>官方的 WriteUp 发现这不是预期的解法（可能是出题人忘记过滤<code>*</code>号了<code>==</code>)，这道题的考点其实是一个 sql_mode 参数<br>Oracle 在缺省情况下支持使用 <code>||</code>连接字符串，但是在 MySQL 中缺省不支持 ，MySQL 缺省使用 CONCAT 系列函数来连接字符串。</p>\n<p>可以通过修改<code>sql_mode</code>模式：<code>PIPES_AS_CONCAT</code>来实现将<code>||</code>视为<strong>字符串连接符</strong>而非<strong>或</strong>运算符 .</p>\n<p>因此这里预期的 Payload 是通过修改<code>sql_mode</code>来拿到 Flag，如下</p>\n<p>Payload:<code>1;set sql_mode=PIPES_AS_CONCAT;SELECT 1</code></p>\n<p>拼接后就变成了<code>SELECT 1;set sql_mode=PIPES_AS_CONCAT;SELECT 1 || flag FROM Flag</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"成功页面\"><a href=\"#成功页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"成功页面\"></a>成功页面</h2><p><img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005ZbjyVly1gqr3c539y8j30vm0680ss.jpg\" alt=\"005ZbjyVly1gqr3c539y8j30vm0680ss\"></p>\n","feature":false,"text":" 题目页面 访问页面 分析解题打开页面之后，没有什么思路，然后查看源代码也没有什么思路 然后我就只能百度了 发现了连个 payload *,1 1;set sql_mode=PIPES_AS_CONCAT;SELECT 1 分别的显示结果为 题目源码 其实主要就是 SQL 查询语...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":658,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"CTF","slug":"CTF","count":8,"path":"api/categories/CTF.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Web","slug":"Web","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Web.json"},{"name":"Sql Injection","slug":"Sql-Injection","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Sql-Injection.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目页面</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">访问页面</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E8%A7%A3%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分析解题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目源码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">成功页面</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"小巳","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/13/T2mPhMs8rolpWbS.png","link":